- Following up of trades until their settlement for Equities and FI products in US market;
- Contacting counterparties to check that our instructions coincide with theirs to facilitate settlement;
- Training and supervision of colleagues; 
- Analysis and implementation of enhancements;
- Fails follow up: contacting counterparties, clients and agents;
- Regular checks on position and cash accounts. Check breaks between market settlements and internal books and records.

- Analysis of economic indicators of Argentina and Latin America; 
- Reading, interpreting and writing reports on relevant economic issues; 
- Database maintenance.

